  "prompt": "Is there a way on Quora to report individual answers as spam?",
  "response": "Yes, on Quora, you can report individual answers as spam. Here\u2019s how you can do it:\n\n1. **Locate the Answer**: Find the answer that you believe is spam.\n2. **Click the Three Dots**: Look for the three dots (typically vertical) at the bottom right corner of the answer.\n3. **Select \u201cReport\u201d**: Click on \u201cReport\u201d from the menu that appears.\n4. **Choose the Reason**: Choose the option that best fits why you are reporting the answer, such as \u201cSpam\u201d.\n\nAfter you report an answer, Quora's moderation team will review it and take appropriate action. Your report helps maintain the quality of content on the platform.",
